issue.body:
### Search before asking

- [X] I had searched in the [issues](https://github.com/apache/eventmesh/issues?q=is%3Aissue) and found no similar issues.


### Environment

Windows

### EventMesh version

master

### What happened

![image](https://github.com/apache/eventmesh/assets/41445332/d0150ac7-e95e-478d-af0c-e85b00889512)


### How to reproduce

```
{
    "callbackPath":"/webhook/github/eventmesh/all",
    "manufacturerName":"github",
    "manufacturerDomain":"www.github.com",
    "manufacturerEventName":"all",
    "cloudEventName":"github-eventmesh",
    "secret": "testSecret"
}
```

### Debug logs

_No response_
